=Description=

" Sophia Parker discusses a pamphlet published last year "The journey to the Interface". She discusses how users of public services such as Education and Health can inform how those services are designed and used - an approach that is "less about competition and contestability, and more about closing the gap between what people want and need, and what service organisations do"."
